    "elements": [
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "(6-11) The tribe of Benjamin.",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "p",
        "class": "",
        "text": "(6) Benjamin.—Before this word bnê (sons of . . .) has been lost, because Benjamin in Hebrew begins with the same three letters. The present list of the sons of Benjamin may be compared with three others, that of Gen. xlvi 21, that of Num. xxvi 38-41, and that of the next 1chron 1Chronicles 7:1-5.",
