        "element": "span",
        "class": "cmt_word",
        "text": "Jediael",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ", three. We have four passages for our authorities as to the sons of Benjamin, and it is not altogether easy to bring them into verbal harmony. They are ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "verse-link",
        "text": "Genesis 46:21",
        "children": []
